         <abstract>
            <p>Polynomials orthogonal on $\lbrack 0, \infty \rbrack$ with regard to the weight function $w(x) = x^a(1 + x)^{-\beta}$ are obtained, recurrence relations are found and the differential equation, which is satisfied by them, is given. Formulas for weights and abscissas in the corresponding quadrature formula are given.</p>
          </abstract>
